#. <section class="sutta" id="sn8.2"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn8.2:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 8"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 8"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn8.2:0.2"
msgid "1. Vaṅgīsavagga"
msgstr "1. With Vaṅgīsa"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 2. Aratīsutta → aratisuttaṃ (bj, s1-3) | arai (pts1)
msgctxt "sn8.2:0.3"
msgid "2. Aratīsutta"
msgstr "2. Dissatisfaction"

# The pe seems odd here.
#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.401"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn8.2:1.1"
msgid ""
"Ekaṃ samayaṃ … pe … āyasmā vaṅgīso āḷaviyaṃ viharati aggāḷave cetiye "
"āyasmatā nigrodhakappena upajjhāyena saddhiṃ."
msgstr ""
"At one time Venerable Vaṅgīsa was staying near Āḷavī, at the Aggāḷava Tree-"
"shrine, together with his mentor, Venerable Nigrodhakappa."

msgctxt "sn8.2:1.2"
msgid ""
"Tena kho pana samayena āyasmā nigrodhakappo pacchābhattaṃ "
"piṇḍapātapaṭikkanto vihāraṃ pavisati, sāyaṃ vā nikkhamati aparajju vā kāle."
msgstr ""
"Now at that time after Venerable Nigrodhakappa had finished his meal, on his "
"return from alms-round, he would enter his dwelling and not emerge for the "
"rest of that day, or the next."

msgctxt "sn8.2:1.3"
msgid ""
"Tena kho pana samayena āyasmato vaṅgīsassa anabhirati uppannā hoti, rāgo "
"cittaṃ anuddhaṃseti."
msgstr ""
"And at that time Venerable Vaṅgīsa became dissatisfied, as lust infected his "
"mind."

msgctxt "sn8.2:1.4"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmato vaṅgīsassa etadahosi:"
msgstr "Then he thought:"

msgctxt "sn8.2:1.5"
msgid ""
"“alābhā vata me, na vata me lābhā; dulladdhaṃ vata me, na vata me suladdhaṃ; "
msgstr "“It’s my loss, my misfortune, "

msgctxt "sn8.2:1.6"
msgid ""
"yassa me anabhirati uppannā, rāgo cittaṃ anuddhaṃseti; taṃ kutettha labbhā, "
"yaṃ me paro anabhiratiṃ vinodetvā abhiratiṃ uppādeyya."
msgstr ""
"that I’ve become dissatisfied, with lust infecting my mind. How is it "
"possible for someone else to dispel my discontent and give rise to "
"satisfaction?"

msgctxt "sn8.2:1.7"
msgid ""
"Yannūnāhaṃ attanāva attano anabhiratiṃ vinodetvā abhiratiṃ uppādeyyan”ti."
msgstr "Why don’t I do it myself?”"

msgctxt "sn8.2:1.8"
msgid ""
"Atha kho āyasmā vaṅgīso attanāva attano anabhiratiṃ vinodetvā abhiratiṃ "
"uppādetvā tāyaṃ velāyaṃ imā gāthāyo abhāsi:"
msgstr ""
"Then, on the occasion of dispelling his own discontent and giving rise to "
"satisfaction, he recited these verses:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn8.2:2.1"
msgid "“Aratiñca ratiñca pahāya,"
msgstr "“Giving up discontent and desire,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn8.2:2.2"
msgid "Sabbaso gehasitañca vitakkaṃ;"
msgstr "along with all thoughts of the lay life,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn8.2:2.3"
msgid "Vanathaṃ na kareyya kuhiñci,"
msgstr "they wouldn’t get entangled in anything;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn8.2:2.4"
msgid "Nibbanatho arato sa hi bhikkhu."
msgstr "unentangled, undesiring: that’s a real mendicant."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn8.2:3.1"
msgid "Yamidha pathaviñca vehāsaṃ,"
msgstr "Whether on this earth or in the sky,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn8.2:3.2"
msgid "Rūpagatañca jagatogadhaṃ;"
msgstr "whatever in the world is included in form"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn8.2:3.3"
msgid "Kiñci parijīyati sabbamaniccaṃ,"
msgstr "wears out, it is all impermanent;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn8.2:3.4"
msgid "Evaṃ samecca caranti mutattā."
msgstr "the wise live having comprehended this truth."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.402"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
#. VAR: gadhitāse → gadhitā (pts1)
msgctxt "sn8.2:4.1"
msgid "Upadhīsu janā gadhitāse,"
msgstr "People are bound to their attachments,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn8.2:4.2"
msgid "Diṭṭhasute paṭighe ca mute ca;"
msgstr "to what is seen, heard, felt, and thought."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn8.2:4.3"
msgid "Ettha vinodaya chandamanejo,"
msgstr "Unstirred, dispel desire for these things;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn8.2:4.4"
msgid "Yo ettha na limpati taṃ munimāhu."
msgstr "for one called ‘a sage’ does not cling to them."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts1ed" id="pts1ed1.187"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn8.2:5.1"
msgid "Atha saṭṭhinissitā savitakkā,"
msgstr "Attached to the sixty wrong views, and full of their own opinions,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn8.2:5.2"
msgid "Puthū janatāya adhammā niviṭṭhā;"
msgstr "ordinary people are fixed in wrong principles."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn8.2:5.3"
msgid "Na ca vaggagatassa kuhiñci,"
msgstr "But that mendicant wouldn’t join a sectarian group,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn8.2:5.4"
msgid "No pana duṭṭhullabhāṇī sa bhikkhu."
msgstr "still less would they utter lewd speech."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "sn8.2:6.1"
msgid "Dabbo cirarattasamāhito,"
msgstr "Clever, long trained in immersion,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn8.2:6.2"
msgid "Akuhako nipako apihālu;"
msgstr "free of deceit, disciplined, without longing,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn8.2:6.3"
msgid "Santaṃ padaṃ ajjhagamā muni paṭicca,"
msgstr "the sage has reached the state of peace;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn8.2:6.4"
msgid "Parinibbuto kaṅkhati kālan”ti."
msgstr "and because he’s extinguished, he awaits his time.”"
